description:
In this week’s episode of “Unqualified,” the gang welcomes a long-time friend: Lisa Kudrow!  Listen in as Anna and Lisa reminisce about Anna’s guest-starring role on the final season of Friends.  Then, in the most off-the-wall “Rapid Fire” series yet, Anna and Lisa deliberate about whether an Emmy or a SAG Award trophy is the deadlier weapon.  Anna, Sim, and Lisa also talk to a woman who wants to know whether she should remain friends with a man for whom she has feelings, or whether it is time to move on.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
